  "name": "Divine Vessel",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "systems/pf1/icons/skills/light_05.jpg",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Whenever you are the target of a divine spell, you can, as a swift action, grant each ally within 15 feet of you a divine boon. This boon grants a +2 bonus on the next attack roll, skill check, or ability check made before the end of their next turn. You can use this ability a number of times per day equal to 3 + your Wisdom modifier.</p>\n<p>This power replaces the Hand of the Acolyte power of the Arcane Domain.</p>"
